{"tid":2120291,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過無啦啦有個好耐冇見嘅人搵返你","createTime":"2020-07-22T14:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T16:52:35.000Z","uid":363117,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3af86290f3a1063bcb3559a6f947e703f8e8baa4","tid":2120291,"uid":363117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:48:19.000Z","msg":"我先，但我係搵人嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前係同學，唔熟，一路直至畢業都冇乜點講過嘢，互相有對方fb但都唔會傾偈<br />\n<br />\n當年喺學校已經有啲在意呢個人，但因為一路都唔熟，又冇send開message，畢咗業更加冇理由突然搵，然後佢去埋外國發展<br />\n<br />\n咁就過咗差唔多10年，呢段期間最多只係fb/ig post comment講一兩句，講緊可能一年先得一次。直至有一年我去咗佢所在嘅國家生活一段時間，終於鼓起勇氣同佢講「咦？你仲喺度做緊嘢呀，我依家又喺度喎，出唔出嚟食個飯」<br />\n<br />\n之後我哋見左幾次面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來我返咗嚟，直至而家都係間唔中send下message咁。未來會點，我諗要到下次再有機會見面先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n講咁耐其實想問如果有人咁樣無啦啦搵返你會唔會覺得好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路都唔知佢嗰陣係以咩心態同我見面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51033871ed29e6708c8d6b2766809bcaa64890da","tid":2120291,"uid":71237,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"有朋自遠方來，不是保險，便是傳銷。"},{"pid":"a4332100b9def51a5e642cd5769d51aac9d067f8","tid":2120291,"uid":321637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"51033871ed29e6708c8d6b2766809bcaa64890da","tid":2120291,"uid":71237,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"有朋自遠方來，不是保險，便是傳銷。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:54:28.000Z","msg":"或者是紅炸彈"},{"pid":"7184ab154773f9d47d37513c2ea4864934d41305","tid":2120291,"uid":343770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:06:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face